guarded formula characterizing all counter-examples:
"∃ d k l h #keyUse.
  (UseKey( d, k, h, l ) @ #keyUse)
 ∧
  ∀ #keyInit. (InitKey( d, k, h, l ) @ #keyInit) ⇒ ¬(#keyInit < #keyUse)"
*/
by sorry

